{
  "stem": "4122.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I really didn't have nowhere to turn, so I accepted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where shall I go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What will I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They brought out water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I washed up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they brought me a bowl of soup [CRYING] and a piece of bread, milk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[CRYING] And he said, I will come out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Remain here in this field.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I will come out every day, and I will bring you something to eat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And maybe we will find some kind of a place for you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't know those people, but people knew my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They probably knew maybe me, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But my father they knew because he was a businessman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they knew-- And he said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I will bring you every night something here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I didn't have nowhere left to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was there in this field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he used to bring me, though, every day some food, and-- until the corns, they had to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know how do you say, they take it off, and they thresh this, this everything.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were only, like, potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Potatoes grow low, so you cannot hide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, but I was-- but they so thick that I used to hide sometimes there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said that now it's not so danger-- I used to run in the daytime to the forest there and hide, like, under trees, sitting or somewhere when I hear somebody's coming.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And for a few months he was bringing me some food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I never trust him.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
